00:00:12.953 --> 00:00:16.971
Hi! Welcome to your favorite show Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:27.495 --> 00:00:34.420
Today we are going to learn how to cook Special Karapoosa

00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:40.057
Ingredients required for Putnala Murukulu

00:00:40.957 --> 00:00:47.098
Roasted Gram Dal Flour, Gram Flour, Ajowan Seeds,
 Salt, Red Chilli Powder &amp; Oil

00:01:00.731 --> 00:01:10.199
First, heat some oil in a pan

00:01:15.196 --> 00:01:41.762
Take a bowl and add some gram flour, roasted gram dal flour,
 red chilli powder, ajowan seeds, salt and some water into the bowl 

00:01:43.760 --> 00:01:51.090
Now mix them well until it turns into a dough

00:02:14.307 --> 00:02:19.285
Now fill the dough into a dough squeezer

00:02:23.956 --> 00:02:34.046
Now squeeze the dough into the pan &amp; 
deep fry them until they turn into golden brown in colour

00:02:40.758 --> 00:02:43.742
Now remove the fried savouries into a serving plate

